sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Claude
    participant SessionHook as arckit-session hook
    participant VersionFile as arckit-plugin/VERSION
    participant Command as /arckit:requirements
    
    User->>Claude: Start new session
    Claude->>SessionHook: Trigger SessionStart event
    SessionHook->>VersionFile: Read VERSION file (once)
    VersionFile-->>SessionHook: "3.1.2"
    SessionHook->>SessionHook: Export ARCKIT_VERSION=3.1.2
    SessionHook-->>Claude: Inject additionalContext:<br/>"ARCKIT_VERSION=3.1.2"
    
    Note over Claude: Context available for entire session
    
    User->>Claude: /arckit:requirements
    Claude->>Command: Execute with {ARCKIT_VERSION} from context
    Command->>Command: Template footer replacement:<br/>"Generated by ArcKit 3.1.2"
    Command-->>User: Document with embedded version
    
    Note over SessionHook,VersionFile: Hook runs ONCE per session<br/>(not per command)
